%header
	%h2
		Connect with Robert W. McGee

	%p
		Are you a fan of my work? Follow me on social media and check out my Youtube videos.
		You can also subscribe to my newsletter or just send me an email.

	%ul.icons
		%li
			%a.icon-facebook{:href => "https://www.facebook.com/RobertWMcGeeOfficial"}

		%li
			%a.icon-googleplus{:href => "https://plus.google.com/+RobertMcGeePhD"}

		%li
			%a.icon-youtube{:href => "https://www.youtube.com/user/33160Bob"}

		%li
			%a.icon-goodreads{:href => "http://www.goodreads.com/author/show/1222570.Robert_W_McGee"}

		%li
